00:30:03.430 --> 00:30:04.263
- Yeah, that's
- I'd just be

00:30:04.263 --> 00:30:05.570
he looking for that back cut every time.

00:30:05.570 --> 00:30:07.237
- That's the back door step, right.

00:30:07.237 --> 00:30:09.630
So, but that helped me game plan.

00:30:09.630 --> 00:30:12.090
So, these players now play
accidental basketball.

00:30:12.090 --> 00:30:14.550
It drives me to feel crazy because it's

00:30:14.550 --> 00:30:15.980
all penetrating pitch.

00:30:15.980 --> 00:30:17.530
You may make a shot, you may not.

00:30:17.530 --> 00:30:19.840
You have no idea who's
gonna be open or whatever.

00:30:19.840 --> 00:30:20.970
It's accidental basketball.

00:30:20.970 --> 00:30:22.870
We play basketball with purpose.

00:30:22.870 --> 00:30:25.350
If I got the ball, if
their fish is on the wing,

00:30:25.350 --> 00:30:28.950
I'm at the top, I know by (mumbles)

00:30:28.950 --> 00:30:30.970
that you guys like to deny the top.

00:30:30.970 --> 00:30:32.930
All right, cool, deny the top,

00:30:32.930 --> 00:30:34.780
I'll move up a little
bit more, drag you out,

00:30:34.780 --> 00:30:37.020
