00:32:02.270 --> 00:32:04.240
He don't look like he wanna stop.

00:32:04.240 --> 00:32:07.220
He still wanna get 100 if he can.

00:32:07.220 --> 00:32:08.920
Where does that mentality come from,

00:32:08.920 --> 00:32:11.340
where you see most guys,
30, 40 and they chill out,

00:32:11.340 --> 00:32:13.090
like all right, I got this?

00:32:13.090 --> 00:32:15.640
- No, it's a competition.

00:32:15.640 --> 00:32:17.150
My mission is to destroy you.

00:32:17.150 --> 00:32:19.100
It's to, it's not, you know,
I mean, like I don't see it.

00:32:19.100 --> 00:32:22.720
You know like, we're playing,
I'm not stopping at 30.

00:32:22.720 --> 00:32:24.730
I'm gonna keep going until you figure out

00:32:24.730 --> 00:32:26.950
