I'm gonna keep going.

00:32:26.950 --> 00:32:30.351
And that New York game, I
knew D'antoni's philosophy,

00:32:30.351 --> 00:32:32.427
(mumbles) double got us hot.

00:32:32.427 --> 00:32:34.860
Because he always thinks they're
gonna cool off eventually.

00:32:34.860 --> 00:32:35.900
Right, so I understood that.

00:32:35.900 --> 00:32:38.120
So, once I got rolling, I knew
that was gonna be the case.

00:32:38.120 --> 00:32:40.950
But then, watching Phil
leading into the game,

00:32:40.950 --> 00:32:42.550
I knew Wilson.

00:32:42.550 --> 00:32:45.080
I knew he was just gonna
play sound defense.

00:32:45.080 --> 00:32:46.920
Right, he wasn't gonna gamble.

00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:48.420
He wasn't gonna try to block a shot.

00:32:48.420 --> 00:32:51.340
He's gonna try to play
a good position defense.

00:32:51.340 --> 00:32:53.370
So I knew I could get a good look.

00:32:53.370 --> 00:32:54.447
So, from that standpoint,
I said, all right,

00:32:54.447 --> 00:32:57.040
you gotta take more time, be
on balance, knock them down.

00:32:57.040 --> 00:32:59.440
- I was trying to, yo, at some point,

00:32:59.440 --> 00:33:01.970
