gotta put him in the first row.

00:33:01.970 --> 00:33:03.890
Put him right in form of Spike Lee's lap.

00:33:03.890 --> 00:33:05.900
I go there pumping him up.

00:33:05.900 --> 00:33:08.560
He talking, but my boy,
he aint saying nothing.

00:33:08.560 --> 00:33:10.360
He's just out there
being a good young boy.

00:33:10.360 --> 00:33:11.480
He gon' play hard.

00:33:11.480 --> 00:33:14.320
Spike Lee out here getting them going.

00:33:14.320 --> 00:33:15.800
How are you gon' talk to this man?

00:33:15.800 --> 00:33:17.980
You aint gotta check him.

00:33:17.980 --> 00:33:20.113
I was on the bench furious,
like, come on dude.

00:33:20.113 --> 00:33:22.630
You gotta, this man shooting for cash,

00:33:22.630 --> 00:33:26.330
Mark turning and looking and
Spike's (mumbles) (chuckles)

00:33:26.330 --> 00:33:28.410
listen, just running
back, I'm just like, bro,

00:33:28.410 --> 00:33:30.570
this is not cool.

00:33:30.570 --> 00:33:32.310
- That was one of those old moments, man,

00:33:32.310 --> 00:33:34.630
where things happen and
just led to that big moment.

00:33:34.630 --> 00:33:37.610
But like Andrew Bynum, we
just lost the game before.

00:33:37.610 --> 00:33:39.280
He had a injury against Memphis.

00:33:39.280 --> 00:33:41.970
It's, so I'm like, we just
lost to the Celtics 08.

00:33:41.970 --> 00:33:42.840
We think we got Andrew.

00:33:42.840 --> 00:33:44.040
It's gonna make a big difference for us.

00:33:44.040 --> 00:33:45.170
