00:34:00.523 --> 00:34:02.750
I understand, it's hard, you went down.

00:34:02.750 --> 00:34:04.640
But damn it, we're getting it done.

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:07.290
So, it's important to
get into that mind frame

00:34:07.290 --> 00:34:10.510
