don't wanna talk to nobody,

00:34:10.510 --> 00:34:12.190
I don't wanna see those
celebrities on the side line,

00:34:12.190 --> 00:34:14.290
don't dab me, don't say hi to me.

00:34:14.290 --> 00:34:16.545
I don't care about none of
y'all tonight. (chuckles)

00:34:16.545 --> 00:34:18.040
Yeah, you're just focused.
- That was it.

00:34:18.040 --> 00:34:21.960
- Was that also part of like
you was coming into the garden

00:34:21.960 --> 00:34:24.500
