deflated and it was like,

00:34:31.010 --> 00:34:33.900
no, we're going, we're getting it done.

00:34:33.900 --> 00:34:36.030
I understand injury how it sucks.

00:34:36.030 --> 00:34:37.950
But we gotta keep on moving.

00:34:37.950 --> 00:34:39.160
And I had to find that space.

00:34:39.160 --> 00:34:40.580
I didn't go out to dinner in New York.

00:34:40.580 --> 00:34:41.763
