how he got into character

00:34:54.680 --> 00:34:57.310
and how he just became all consuming.

00:34:57.310 --> 00:35:00.190
I was like, that inspired me
to go into my garden mode.

00:35:00.190 --> 00:35:02.130
While I go in there, I don't
wanna say hi to the janitor.

00:35:02.130 --> 00:35:03.080
I don't wanna say hi to these people.

00:35:03.080 --> 00:35:04.630
I don't wanna talk to nobody.

00:35:04.630 --> 00:35:06.216
Everybody leave me alone.

00:35:06.216 --> 00:35:08.420
- That, ever since I seen you, like,

00:35:08.420 --> 00:35:10.680
highlights of you in high
school all the way up

00:35:10.680 --> 00:35:12.180
to the end of your career,

00:35:12.180 --> 00:35:14.703
you always been a aggressive (mumbles).

00:35:14.703 --> 00:35:15.830
Like, what did you learn?

00:35:15.830 --> 00:35:19.060
Who installed aggression in you to,

00:35:19.060 --> 00:35:20.010
- I don't know, man.
